			<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"></h2><h3 id="h3-人材を大切に" style="margin: 30px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(36, 40, 42); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans&quot;, ヒラギノ角ゴシック, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, Roboto, メイリオ, Meiryo, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit;">「人材」を大切に</span></h3>		</div>
